F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">3. Proposal page limits and layout:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;Please refer to Part B of the standard proposal template.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>Character and page limits:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 40 pages for calls for low value grants (EUR 60 000 or below) and 70 for all other cases. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; minimum font size &mdash; Arial 9 points <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; page size: A4</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; margins (top, bottom, left and right): at least 15 mm (not including headers &amp; footers).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluation<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Evaluation criteria, scoring, threshold and process are described in the Call document.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><a href=\"https://europa.eu/youth/sites/default/files/european_solidarity_corps_guide_2022.pdf\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: -24px;\"><span lang=\"EN-IE\" style=\"color: blue;\">european_solidarity_corps_guide_2022.pdf</span></a><font color=\"#0000ff\">&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX:C2021/464/05\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"FR-BE\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">EUR-Lex - C2021/464/05 - EN - EUR-Lex (europa.eu)</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; Indicative timetable for evaluation and grant agreement:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> as described in the Call document.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Publication of the call:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 December 2021<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Deadline for submitting applications:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>May, 3</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;2022 17:00 (Brussels Time)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Evaluation period:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"mso-tab-count:3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>May - September 2022<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quo